---

<section class="section" id="how">
  <div class="section-label">// How it works</div>
  <h2>FOUR STEPS.<br />ZERO WORK.</h2>
  <div class="steps fade-in">
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">01</span>
      <div class="step-icon">&#x1f517;</div>
      <h3>Connect Your Store</h3>
      <p>Paste your Amazon listing, Shopify URL, G2 profile, or Trustpilot page. We do the rest — no CSV exports, no copy-pasting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">02</span>
      <div class="step-icon">&#x1f9e0;</div>
      <h3>AI Picks the Best</h3>
      <p>Claude reads every review and scores them for meme-ability — funny, relatable, punchy. Only the gold ones make the cut.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">03</span>
      <div class="step-icon">&#x1f3ad;</div>
      <h3>Memes Get Made</h3>
      <p>Memelord AI generates trending meme formats around each review. Image memes, video memes, platform-specific captions — all ready to post.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">04</span>
      <div class="step-icon">&#x1f4ec;</div>
      <h3>Newsletter Drops</h3>
      <p>Every week a fully written newsletter lands in your inbox with the meme pack baked in. Forward it, send it, schedule it. Done.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 48px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      margin-top: 64px;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .step {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .step {
      padding: 40px 32px;
      border-bottom: none;
      border-right: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    .step:nth-child(2) {
      border-right: none;
    }

    .step:nth-child(3),
    .step:nth-child(4) {
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    .step:nth-child(4) {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .step {
      border-right: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-top: none;
    }

    .step:nth-child(2) {
      border-right: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    .step:nth-child(3) {
      border-top: none;
    }

    .step:last-child {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  .step:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .step:hover {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 48px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #e8e0d5;
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .step-num {
      font-size: 64px;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
    }
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--orange-pale);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ffc4a8;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
